<span class=title>   I want to create a warrior community, need input</span><hr size=1> If you're like me, you read the class specific message boards such as The Safehouse, Druid's Grove, Everquest monks etc every few days, long ago however I noticed there isn't a good message board for the Warrior class, the stratics board is ok, however I feel it lacks the community feel of the other sites, and I personally prefer the ezboard layout. Because of these, and my knowledge about the class, I have decided to create a message board to fill this gap, it will be small at first but hopefully one day it will be as great as The Safehouse etc. Here is what i'm looking for. I am planning to have a loose moderation policy but no personal attacks of any kind will be permitted.<br>
<br>
I want to know what YOU want in a warrior class message board.<br>
<br>
I would also be interested if some people who are knowledgable about the class would like to contribute.<br>
<br>
Thanks <p>Nillon, level 55 Myrmidon, Brell Serilis</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/unillon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nillon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>GD RPers</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/24/00 8:53:44 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/soj/itsme.jpg height=108 width=82></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I want to create a warrior community, need input</span><hr size=1> prototype is up at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub20.ezboard.com/beverquestwarriors33689">pub20.ezboard.com/beverqu...riors33689</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> , tell me what you think. <p>Nillon, level 55 Myrmidon, Brell Serilis</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/umidibrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Midi Brell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/24/00 10:42:47 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.animfactory.com/animgifs/creatures/animals3/dog/dogdrinking_sm_wht.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ss</span><hr size=1> Is the swordstrike site still up?  Dunno if they had a mssg board though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/uthoricofbrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thoric of Brell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/24/00 2:31:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ss</span><hr size=1> I'd probably add a forum for matters of general interest that appl